source.name: HUD Administrative Law Judges Decisions
source.description: This site contains substantive and precedential decisions issued by the Office of Administrative Law Judges. The site does not contain subsequent rulings or determinations which may have been issued: (1) by the HUD Secretary following Secretary review of an ALJ decision; or (2) by a federal court of the United States upon review or appeal of a final agency action. Therefore, decisions found at this site do not necessarily represent the final disposition of the case.
